== 成员名单 ==
社团成员名单和曲目staff为匿名。这里列出已知道的信息。<ref>信息来源于VGMdb管理员Illidan。 https://vgmdb.net/forums/showpost.php?p=72283&postcount=8</ref>
<!-- The circle keeps its list of members as well as track credits anonymous. However, the member list is availble thanks to VGMdb admin Illidan's research, including guest guitarist. A tentative list of tracks that S.S.H. is responsible for on these albums exists thanks to VGMdb user layzee. Note that Eru's says they're part of the circle on Aether's site as well as his Twitter bio. The circle's albums on DLsite are also credited as Aether&Hellion Sounds. -->
* [[Eru]] （[[Aether]]）
* [[姫川紫音]] （[[LOST IN THE DARKNESS]]）
* [[あず♪]] （[[君の美術館]]）
* [[稲井ゆう]] （[[PHOENIX Project]]）
* [[S.S.H.]]（[[埼玉最終兵器]]）

[[高瀬]] （[[まぐなむお～ぱす]]）和[[Godspeed]] （[[ViViX]]）也以guest身份参加社团的第一张专辑''The Sentence of Death''。

